OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1774854330
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Mon 13 Apr to Mon 27 Apr
OL,6,FHigh pressure may be dominant early in
OL,7,Fthis period, which would bring plenty
OL,8,Fof dry and settled weather across the
OL,9,FUK, especially in the south and
OL,10,Fperhaps east. Any low pressure systems
OL,11,Fbringing wetter, windier weather are
OL,12,Fmost likely to affect the north.
OL,13,FTowards the latter part of April, low
OL,14,Fpressure patterns may become more
OL,15,Fprevalent, with unsettled or more
OL,16,Fchangeable conditions developing
OL,17,Fwidely. Temperatures are likely to be
OL,18,Fclose to or slightly above normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
